705006f-a.title: Brooklyn: Hubbard Place - 40th Street (East)
705006f-a.text:
4011 Hubbard Place, north side, just east of East 40th Street, kown
once as Ho. 8 Hubbard Place, showing the R. Woolsey House, occupied by the
Woolsey family from 1857 to 1873.
